{"tid":2321794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【3個新郎】3個男人結婚共譜愛情故事　新郎媽媽榮升開通奶奶︰會照顧3個仔","createTime":"2020-12-11T20:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T08:57:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"00c604f669f6c68bc21fc23ed550770c204a304e","tid":2321794,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T20:50:13.000Z","msg":"同性婚姻愈來愈多人接受，泰國有男同志亦拉埋天窗，更是非常特別的3人行婚禮，引起當地群眾注目。3名分別30歲、24歲及22歲的男同志在婚禮上得到眾多親友祝福，其中一名新郎的媽媽還表示對婚事感到高興，承諾會好好照顧及保護這3個孩子。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國傳媒《Matichon Online》報道，現年30歲的醫院營養師James Chandmthong，7年前在網上結識了22歲舞蹈員Nong Amsapchan，開始了愛情長跑，後來在社交網站認識了24歲、亦為舞蹈員的Nong Toei Buutawat，3人互相過電，決定共譜三人行的愛情故事。<br />\n<br />\n3男同居已久彼此是家人<br />\n3人同居已久，共同分擔家務與開支，早已當彼此是家人，他們更共同創辦了名為「Thanawat Dance」的舞蹈團體。<br />\n<br />\n他們認為這段3人行愛情已經成熟，決定攜手進入新階段組織家庭，於12月8日舉辦3男婚禮，在眾多親友及長老見證下，以當地佛教傳統儀式完婚。<br />\n<br />\n新郎媽媽︰會照顧好3個孩子<br />\n對於3人行的愛情，Amsapchan的媽媽Thanayarat Phol表示理解和感到高興，自己就像多了2名兒子，揚言會好好照顧這3個孩子。<br />\n&quot;希望他們能夠像其他家庭一樣，繼續過著快樂的生活。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826289/3men_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826289%2F3men_01_1024.jpg&h=eb2cafd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826289/3men_04_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826289%2F3men_04_1024.jpg&h=f6031cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826289/3men_18a_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826289%2F3men_18a_1024.jpg&h=508023b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2826289/3men_20a_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2826289%2F3men_20a_1024.jpg&h=72a457f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5180c20f2a5851b1b00fac0f5d596c99bdb6de32","tid":2321794,"uid":325346,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T20:53:19.000Z","msg":"3P is awesome"},{"pid":"e377666fc68c209088ffdbf792c874cf239aefec","tid":2321794,"uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T20:56:00.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386ee299d504ad158230051cbc90936cac49bfbe","tid":2321794,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T21:36:58.000Z","msg":"好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n恭喜晒"},{"pid":"81116c564769e4df735b785c8b70bec6aaf48790","tid":2321794,"uid":33874,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T22:15:29.000Z","msg":"人型蜈蚣"},{"pid":"236a0c7855d5718a56893ed07cf9e93da654aa7d","tid":2321794,"uid":121076,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T22:18:09.000Z","msg":"中間果個咪爽死"},{"pid":"ffed06f6f476d6ddafd7ca6033d8a945d0b707d7","tid":2321794,"uid":297230,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T22:19:20.000Z","msg":"睇住d人玩壞呢d咁嘅制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065898ef6ba9f557caf3bb09501ae089443ca6a8","tid":2321794,"uid":128087,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T22:31:00.000Z","msg":"一夫多夫制"},{"pid":"be864da274c533ec89976089b1fd77a8c49e9f8f","tid":2321794,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T22:35:23.000Z","msg":"wtf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"